messages.text: Hello, I need help with my order.
Sure, I can assist you with that!
Can I return a product?
Yes, returns are possible within 30 days.
What are your business hours?
We are open from 9 AM to 5 PM, Monday to Friday.
I forgot my password.
Please use the 'Forgot Password' link to reset it.
Do I get a discount?
Yes, Gold members get a 10% discount.
How can I change my contact preference?
You can change it in your account settings.
When will my order arrive?
Your order is expected to arrive by next week.
Is my subscription still active?
Yes, your subscription is active until the end of the month.
I want to see my purchase history.
Currently, your purchase history is empty.
I just wanted to say thank you for the great service.
Thank you for your feedback!

posts.content: I love Python because of its simplicity.
Java is the best due to its portability.
Practice coding every day.
Read more books on algorithms.
VSCode is versatile and powerful.
I prefer using WebStorm.
Front-end is more visual and creative.
Back-end is the backbone of a project.
Use console.log() and breakpoints.
Always check for syntax errors first.

test_cases.threadTitle: Is AI going to replace developers?

posts.content: AI will assist, not replace.
AI may automate some jobs.

test_cases.threadTitle: Best resources to learn machine learning?

posts.content: Coursera and Udacity have great courses.
I recommend reading 'Hands-On Machine Learning with Scikit-Learn, Keras, and TensorFlow'.

test_cases.threadTitle: Should I learn HTML before JavaScript?

posts.content: Yes, HTML is fundamental for web development.
You can start with JavaScript, but knowing HTML helps.

test_cases.threadTitle: What's the best way to manage state in React?

posts.content: Use React hooks and context API for simple state management.
Redux is still the best for larger applications.

test_cases.threadTitle: How to make a website accessible?

posts.content: Use semantic HTML and ARIA roles.
Test with screen readers and keyboard navigation.
